      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; default level 1 accepted.",
      "rationale": "Statistical characterization of blood sample variability across donors not required at MRL 2. Three replicate experiments per operating point provide basic repeatability evidence. Factor accepted at default level."
